HEADWORD: Culture myth
<hw>Culture myth</hw>. <def>A myth accounting for the discovery of arts
and sciences or the advent of a higher civilization, as in the
Prometheus myth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

